OL,3,CTwo arrested after man presented at
OL,4,Chospital with gunshot injuries
OL,6,FTwo men have been arrested after a man
OL,7,Fpresented at a hospital in Leeds with
OL,8,Fgunshot injuries.
OL,10,FOfficers were called to Leeds General
OL,11,FInfirmary shortly after 5.30pm on
OL,12,FTuesday by hospital staff after a man
OL,13,Fin his late twenties showed gun shot
OL,14,Fwounds.
OL,16,FHis injuries are believed to be non-
OL,17,Flife threatening.
OL,19,FIt sparked a large armed police
OL,20,Fpresence outside the Accident &
OL,21,FEmergency Department.
