OL,3,CTwo arrested after man presented at
OL,4,Chospital with gunshot injuries
OL,6,FThe incident did not occur at the
OL,7,Fhospital or on its grounds but a
OL,8,Fpolice cordon is still in place.
OL,10,FEnquiries are continuing to find out
OL,11,Fthe circumstances of what took place
OL,12,Fand how the man came to be injured.
